<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>PortFolioPH — Single Page Roadmap</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --fg: #111827;
      --muted: #4b5563;
      --line: #cbd5e1;
      --head: #0f172a;
      --accent: #1d4ed8;
      --bg: #ffffff;
    }

    @page {
      size: A3 landscape;
      margin: 8mm;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      color: var(--fg);
      background: var(--bg);
      font-size: 9px;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }

    .page {
      width: 100%;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-rows: auto auto auto auto auto;
      gap: 6px;
    }

    h1, h2, h3 { margin: 0; }

    .title {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding: 6px 8px;
      background: #f8fafc;
    }

    .title h1 {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--head);
    }

    .title .meta {
      margin-top: 2px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 8.5px;
    }

    .grid-2 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .grid-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2.2fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .card {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding: 5px;
      min-height: 0;
    }

    .card h2 {
      font-size: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      color: var(--head);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      padding-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .tiny { font-size: 8px; color: var(--muted); }

    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      table-layout: fixed;
    }

    th, td {
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      padding: 2px 3px;
      vertical-align: top;
      word-wrap: break-word;
    }

    th {
      background: #eff6ff;
      color: #0b1e59;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .center { text-align: center; }
    .right { text-align: right; }

    ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 12px;
    }

    li { margin: 0 0 1px 0; }

    .sprint-table td { font-size: 8px; }
    .muted { color: var(--muted); }

    .footer-note {
      border: 1px dashed var(--line);
      padding: 4px 6px;
      font-size: 8px;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: #f9fafb;
    }

    @media print {
      html, body { width: 100%; height: 100%; }
      .page { gap: 5px; }
      a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="title">
      <h1>PortFolioPH — Offline/Online Portfolio Builder for Students (Single-Page Print Roadmap)</h1>
      <div class="meta">
        8 Sprints (8 Weeks) • 363 Total Hours • Mark (Dev): 256h • Tom (UX/QA): 55h • Rex (Docs/Pres): 52h • Platform: Flutter Android + SQLite + Firebase + PDF Export
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="grid-3">
      <article class="card">
        <h2>Master Sprint Dashboard</h2>
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th class="center" style="width:5%">#</th>
              <th style="width:9%">Week</th>
              <th style="width:20%">Theme</th>
              <th class="center" style="width:7%">Mark</th>
              <th class="center" style="width:7%">Tom</th>
              <th class="center" style="width:7%">Rex</th>
              <th class="center" style="width:8%">Total</th>
              <th style="width:19%">Demo Milestone</th>
              <th style="width:10%">Dependency</th>
              <th style="width:8%">Risk</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td class="center">1</td><td>Wk 1</td><td>Core Setup & Architecture</td><td class="center">32</td><td class="center">6</td><td class="center">6</td><td class="center">44</td><td>APK with splash, nav, offline DB</td><td>None</td><td>Low</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="center">2</td><td>Wk 2</td><td>Auth + Profile</td><td class="center">32</td><td class="center">7</td><td class="center">6</td><td class="center">45</td><td>Full auth flow + dashboard</td><td>S1</td><td>Low</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="center">3</td><td>Wk 3</td><td>Projects CRUD + Gallery</td><td class="center">32</td><td class="center">6</td><td class="center">6</td><td class="center">44</td><td>Add/edit/delete projects with images</td><td>S2</td><td>Med</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="center">4</td><td>Wk 4</td><td>Media Upload + Certificates</td><td class="center">32</td><td class="center">8</td><td class="center">7</td><td class="center">47</td><td>Certificate CRUD + thumbnails</td><td>S3</td><td>Med</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="center">5</td><td>Wk 5</td><td>Achievements + Reflections</td><td class="center">32</td><td class="center">7</td><td class="center">7</td><td class="center">46</td><td>Complete portfolio data model</td><td>S4</td><td>Med</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="center">6</td><td>Wk 6</td><td>Resume Builder + PDF</td><td class="center">32</td><td class="center">8</td><td class="center">7</td><td class="center">47</td><td>3 templates + PDF export/share</td><td>S5</td><td>High</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="center">7</td><td>Wk 7</td><td>Firebase Sync + Admin</td><td class="center">32</td><td class="center">6</td><td class="center">6</td><td class="center">44</td><td>Online sync + admin + backup</td><td>S6</td><td>High</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="center">8</td><td>Wk 8</td><td>QA, Polish & Release</td><td class="center">32</td><td class="center">7</td><td class="center">7</td><td class="center">46</td><td>Signed APK + capstone demo</td><td>S7</td><td>Low</td></tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="center"><strong>T</strong></td><td colspan="2"><strong>Grand Total</strong></td><td class="center"><strong>256</strong></td><td class="center"><strong>55</strong></td><td class="center"><strong>52</strong></td><td class="center"><strong>363</strong></td><td colspan="3"><strong>Production APK + Documentation + Presentation</strong></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h2>Class Schedule (8 Weeks)</h2>
        <div class="tiny">M/Th 4:00–5:30 PM (3h/wk) + Wed 3:00–5:00 PM (2h/wk) = 7.5h/wk</div>
        <ul>
          <li>W1: init, scaffold, DB, routing, theme, splash</li>
          <li>W2: auth service/screens, profile setup, dashboard</li>
          <li>W3: project CRUD, image storage, detail carousel</li>
          <li>W4: certificate CRUD, picker, thumbnails, permissions</li>
          <li>W5: achievements, reflections, portfolio overview</li>
          <li>W6: resume templates, PDF generation, export/share</li>
          <li>W7: Firebase sync, admin panel, backup/restore, PIN</li>
          <li>W8: regression, fixes, signed APK, capstone demo</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="tiny" style="margin-top:4px;">In-class ≈ 60h • Independent work ≈ 303h</div>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Core:</strong> Flutter, sqflite, provider, go_router</li>
          <li><strong>Storage/Media:</strong> path_provider, image_picker, file_picker, flutter_image_compress</li>
          <li><strong>Security/Auth:</strong> crypto, shared_preferences, permission_handler</li>
          <li><strong>PDF:</strong> pdf, printing, share_plus</li>
          <li><strong>Cloud:</strong> firebase_core, cloud_firestore, firebase_auth</li>
          <li><strong>Polish/Test:</strong> shimmer, mockito</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="tiny" style="margin-top:4px;">Critical checks: API compatibility, font registration for Filipino characters, PDF preview on API 21/28/33, Firebase quota.</div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>Detailed Sprint Work Matrix (All Content Condensed)</h2>
      <table class="sprint-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th style="width:4%" class="center">S</th>
            <th style="width:35%">★ Mark — Development Scope (32h each sprint)</th>
            <th style="width:20%">Tom — UX / QA</th>
            <th style="width:18%">Rex — Docs / Presentation</th>
            <th style="width:23%">Top Risks + Mitigations</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="center">1</td>
            <td>Project init; full clean-architecture scaffold; SQLite DB service + migrations; constants/theme/router; bottom-nav placeholders; splash/session redirect; Android permissions; Git flow; device run + integration test.</td>
            <td>PH CV/portfolio research; low-fi wireframes (5 tabs); emulator smoke test.</td>
            <td>Proposal draft; README setup; shared Drive structure.</td>
            <td>Env setup blockers (front-load setup); schema churn (ERD sign-off); router learning curve (fallback path).</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="center">2</td>
            <td>User model; AuthService register/login + SHA-256; AuthProvider; register/login screens; profile service/setup; dashboard; session persistence; validators/date utils; end-to-end auth flow.</td>
            <td>Mockups for auth/profile/dashboard; 10 auth test scenarios; accessibility checklist.</td>
            <td>Registration flow documentation; architecture chapter; sprint minutes.</td>
            <td>Crypto/API compatibility; image_picker edge cases; workload pressure (strict prioritization).</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="center">3</td>
            <td>Project model/service/provider; image storage/compression; project list/search/pagination; add/edit/detail screens; reusable cards/chips/loading/empty widgets; file utils; CRUD E2E.</td>
            <td>Project category/tag conventions; UI mockups; CRUD testing with sample datasets.</td>
            <td>Module documentation; validation rules; sprint minutes.</td>
            <td>Storage bloat (compress+limit); list perf (pagination); path fragility (relative path strategy).</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="center">4</td>
            <td>Certificate model/service/provider; list/filter/search; add/edit + file/image picker; media manager; thumbnail pipeline; quota indicator; skills CRUD base; permission UX; integration test.</td>
            <td>Certificate/media UX designs; Android storage permission research; multi-version testing.</td>
            <td>Media module documentation; cert-format research; proposal progress update.</td>
            <td>Scoped storage issues (API30+ testing first); thumbnail latency (async placeholders); quota handling (warn thresholds).</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="center">5</td>
            <td>Achievements model/service/provider/screens; reflections model/service/provider/editor; search/filter/privacy; portfolio overview aggregation; skills tracker visuals; module-wide integration test.</td>
            <td>Achievement type research; reflection UX mockups; full-module QA.</td>
            <td>Documentation + diagrams; validation standards; mid-project report.</td>
            <td>Search scaling (index + limit); editor scope creep (plaintext only); aggregate query performance (cached stats).</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="center">6</td>
            <td>Resume model/data mapping; 3 template widgets (Simple/Professional/Modern); PDF service + TTF fonts; PDF layout parity; preview/save/share; live builder controls; export history; E2E export flow.</td>
            <td>Template design review; PH CV format standards; cross-device PDF QA.</td>
            <td>Resume/PDF chapter; mobile PDF best practices; user manual draft.</td>
            <td>Font rendering bugs (register fonts early); oversize files (image compression/no-image option); preview inconsistencies (API matrix tests).</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="center">7</td>
            <td>Firebase init/rules/auth; local-first sync service; dual auth mode; admin setup; admin dashboard/user list; backup export/import with schema validation; PIN auto-lock; SQL sanitization audit; integration flow.</td>
            <td>Firebase quota analysis; offline→online conflict testing; admin/backup QA.</td>
            <td>Admin/sync architecture docs; data privacy compliance section; retrospective notes.</td>
            <td>Quota overrun (emulator/limits); sync conflicts (timestamp strategy + tests); restore corruption (temp-validate-swap).</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="center">8</td>
            <td>Regression testing; service unit tests (≥80% target); widget tests; triaged bug-fix sprint; performance profiling; UI polish (loading/error/empty states); accessibility pass; keystore/signing; release build + device validation; cleanup.</td>
            <td>Final QA matrix (50+ cases); visual consistency review; demo support.</td>
            <td>Finalize capstone paper; deck (15–20 slides); quick-start manual; lessons learned.</td>
            <td>Late critical defects (prioritize C/H severity); APK size risk (split-per-ABI/optimize); keystore loss (multi-backup policy).</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section class="grid-2">
      <article class="card">
        <h2>Database ERD (10 Tables)</h2>
        <div class="tiny">users, projects, project_images, achievements, certificates, reflections, skills, resumes, export_history, audit_log</div>
        <table>
          <thead><tr><th>Core Entity Rules</th><th>Key Notes</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>All tables use INTEGER PK AUTOINCREMENT</td><td>created_at/updated_at timestamps used widely for sync and audits</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Foreign keys centered on <code>users.id</code></td><td>App-level FK enforcement strategy with cascade semantics in service layer</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Portfolio modules separated by concern</td><td>Projects, certificates, achievements, reflections, skills each have isolated services/providers</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Resume/export tables support auditability</td><td>Resume drafts + export logs retained for history and reporting</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h2>Flutter Scaffold Coverage</h2>
        <div class="tiny">Architecture locked from Sprint 1 to avoid import chaos/spaghetti structure.</div>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Config:</strong> app/app router/theme/constants</li>
          <li><strong>Models:</strong> user, project, certificate, achievement, reflection, skill, resume, export_history</li>
          <li><strong>Services:</strong> database, auth, profile, project/media, certificate, achievement, reflection, skill, resume/pdf, sync, backup, security</li>
          <li><strong>Providers:</strong> auth/profile/project/certificate/achievement/reflection/skill/resume</li>
          <li><strong>Screens:</strong> splash, auth, dashboard, profile, portfolio modules, resume builder, export, admin, security</li>
          <li><strong>Widgets/Utils:</strong> cards, carousel, skill bars, template widgets, skeleton loader, validators/date/file/pdf utils</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="grid-2">
      <article class="card">
        <h2>Day 1 Kickoff Checklist (Sprint 1)</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Install SDK/toolchain; verify with health checks.</li>
          <li>Create project and run baseline app.</li>
          <li>Add package manifest dependencies and resolve.</li>
          <li>Create complete folder/file scaffold placeholders.</li>
          <li>Implement constants, theme, router, splash, DB creation.</li>
          <li>Configure Android permissions and device-run smoke test.</li>
          <li>Initialize repository workflow and shared collaboration assets.</li>
          <li>Parallel tracks: Tom (research + wireframes), Rex (proposal + README + docs setup).</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h2>KPI Scorecard</h2>
        <table>
          <thead><tr><th>KPI</th><th>Target</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Developer hours (Mark)</td><td>256h</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Support hours (Tom+Rex)</td><td>107h</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Critical crash rate</td><td>0</td></tr>
            <tr><td>PDF export success</td><td>100% on 2 devices</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Screens implemented</td><td>≥22</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Service test coverage</td><td>≥80%</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Release APK size</td><td>&lt; 50MB</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Sprint deliverables completed</td><td>8/8</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Android support</td><td>API 26–34 validated</td></tr>
            <tr><td>SQLite query latency</td><td>&lt; 50ms</td></tr>
            <tr><td>UI performance</td><td>~60 FPS mid-range device</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Firebase sync success</td><td>100% stable connection tests</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Backup/restore integrity</td><td>100% verified</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Documentation completion</td><td>Capstone chapters 1–5 + 15–20 slides</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="footer-note">
      <strong>Print tip:</strong> Open this file in a browser and print using <em>Landscape</em>, paper size <em>A3</em> (or A4 with “Fit to page”).
      This one-pager consolidates content from: Cover, Dashboard, Sprint 1–8, Master Tracker, Class Schedule, Tech Stack, ERD, Flutter Scaffold, Day 1 Checklist, and Metrics.
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
